//www.nme.com/news/music/heinz-creates-new-condiment-in-honour-of-taylor-swift-and-travis-kelce-3505733">亨氏宣布将推出一款新酱料，以纪念斯威夫特和凯尔斯的浪漫传闻引发的病毒式传播</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sales-of-travis-kelce-chiefs-jerseys-see-400-per-cent-sale-spike-amid-taylor-swift-dating-rumours-3504263">凯尔斯酋长队球衣的购买量最近增加了 400%</a> 。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-fans-react-cornelia-street-sign-kansas-city-chiefs-and-new-york-jets-game-3507551">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 粉丝对堪萨斯城酋长队 (Kansas City Chiefs) 和纽约喷气机队 (New York Jets) 比赛中显示的“Cornelia St”标志的反应</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
