会说话的人物：克里斯·弗朗茨暗示进一步可能重聚https://www.nme.com/news/music/talking-heads-chris-franz-hints-at-further-pottial-reunion-3507373?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=talking-heads-chris-franz-hints-进一步潜在的团聚Elizabeth AubreySun, 01 Oct 2023 21:15:53 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3507373 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Talking-Heads-reunion.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="会说话的头像重聚" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Talking-Heads-reunion.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Talking-Heads-reunion-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Talking-Heads-reunion-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Talking-Heads-reunion-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Talking-Heads-reunion-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Talking-Heads-reunion-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>乐队上个月重聚，重新发行了《Stop Making Sense》</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/talking-heads-chris-franz-hints-at-further-potential-reunion-3507373">《Talking Heads：Chris Franz 暗示进一步重聚的可能性》一文</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Talking-Heads-reunion.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="会说话的头像重聚" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Talking-Heads-reunion.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Talking-Heads-reunion-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Talking-Heads-reunion-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Talking-Heads-reunion-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Talking-Heads-reunion-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Talking-Heads-reunion-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/talking-heads">Talking Heads</a>鼓手 Chris Franz 暗示可能还会有进一步的重聚。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/talking-heads-every-album-ranked-in-order-of-greatness-3486762">Talking Heads：每张专辑按伟大程度排列</a></strong></li></ul><p>这支标志性乐队由弗朗茨、主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-byrne">大卫·伯恩</a>、吉他手杰里·哈里森和贝斯手蒂娜·韦茅斯组成<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/talking-heads-to-reunite-for-qa-at-toronto-international-film-fest-3483906">，本月早些时候，他们 20 多年来首次公开亮相。他们于 9 月 11 日在多伦多国际电影节上重聚并进行问答。</a></p><p>正如 8 月份宣布的那样， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/talking-heads-to-reunite-for-qa-at-toronto-international-film-fest-3483906">这场期待已久的重聚是为了庆祝 Talking Heads 的传奇音乐会电影<em>《Stop Making Sense</em> 》（1984 年）40 周年</a>。</p><p>现在，弗兰茨暗示，在分享了伯恩与韦茅斯的新照片后，可能会进一步重聚。他为图片添加了标题：“一张图片胜过十亿个文字。”您可以<a href="https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=pfbid0ryEEstEjdkBnmVwL92JkQ5hG6TrT8hRhegm6LasT5DEzsGymDzXjuinhVqdbiVFjl&amp;id=1449881301" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>查看完整的帖子。</p><p>去年，弗朗茨<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/talking-heads-chris-frantz-tina-weymouth-2023-remain-in-love-tour-tickets-interview-3350890">在接受<em>NME</em></a>采访时谈到了可能的重聚，他说：“我确实尝试过几次，最后一次是大约 20 年前，在那之后，大卫只是说：‘我从来不想让你问我这个问题再次。我不会解决这个问题。这是一种耻辱，但事实就是如此。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="停止有意义|官方预告片高清 | A24" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-rjMwSTeVeo?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>此前，韦茅斯最近在<a href="https://pitchfork.com/features/interview/talking-heads-reunion-2023-stop-making-sense/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Pitchfork</em></a>的一次新采访中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/talking-heads-on-a-potential-reunion-were-just-savouring-the-moment-3502089">表示，乐队“只是在享受这一刻”，</a>并讨论了乐队全面重聚的可能性。</p><div><p> “我们只是在享受这一刻。我们很高兴它产生了持续 40 年的美好事物。我们并没有真正展望太远的未来，”韦茅斯说。 “我们可能站在街角，一辆公共汽车会把我们撞倒。我们非常高兴我们还活着。我们四个人来这里就是为了享受这一刻。”</p><p>哈里森补充道：“不过，毫无疑问，它重拾了我们在一起的快乐。我认为对于我们每个人来说，观看这部电影时，我们都会感受到快乐——不仅仅是我们四个人，还有舞台上的每个人以及工作人员。这确实牵动着我对每个人的爱的心弦。” </p><div class="td-a-ad id_inline_ad1 id_ad_content-horiz-center"><div class="apester-media apester-unit" data-manual-top-desktop="64" data-manual-top-mobile="55" data-token="5644b81019aec6d348309b65" data-context="true" data-tags="" data-fallback="true"><div id="apester-companion-placement-above-387a947a-37b7-4be9-abcd-306c3bcf17f0" class="apester-companion-above-container"><div id="apester-companion-video-above" class="companion container-video"><div id="apester-companion-video-above-387a947a-37b7-4be9-abcd-306c3bcf17f0" class="apester-ad-container"><div id="apester-companion-video-above-387a947a-37b7-4be9-abcd-306c3bcf17f0gui"><div id="av-container" class=" av-desktop hide-controls"><div id="av-inner"><div id="slot"><div id="preloader"><div class="td-a-ad id_inline_ad0 id_ad_content-horiz-center"><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/david-byrne-regrets-talking-heads-split-i-was-a-little-tyrant-3484618">伯恩最近解释说，他对Talking Heads的解散感到遗憾</a>，并坦言自己当时是一个“小暴君”。</p><p>他还将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/david-byrne-on-talking-heads-current-relationship-divorces-are-never-easy-3496076">自己目前与 Talking Heads 乐队成员的关系比作离婚</a>。</p></div><p> “离婚从来都不是一件容易的事，”他告诉<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/09/09/arts/music/talking-heads-stop-making-sense.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《纽约时报》</em></a> 。 “我们相处得很好。一切都非常亲切等等。我们并不是都是最好的朋友。但每个人都很高兴看到这部电影的回归。”</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/talking-heads-chris-franz-hints-at-further-potential-reunion-3507373">《Talking Heads：Chris Franz 暗示进一步重聚的可能性》一文</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
